title: War of the Roses - I Tried Calling Him 23 Times!
description: Jamie called the show to bring her fiancé, Chris to the hot seat on War of the Roses. Chris had missed 23 calls in the middle of the night with a bunch of voicemails, she ended up waking him up and made him play the voicemails.
